# Indelible Editions.

Series based, Unique Editions with blockchain verfiability on:

* Card Name, example: "Card 3 Name"
* Card No, example: 3
* Card Issuance, example: 27
* Card Edition, example: 6 of 27
* Card Revealed on drop. (true/false)
